        <title>Closet Shelves!</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://dl.dropboxusercontent.com/u/8637739/benwilhelm.com/large/posts/closet-shelves/shelves-in-progress.jpg&quot; title=&quot;Trusty assistant&quot;&gt;
